-expansion of the surface layers of\nG0.253+0.016 as it recedes from the Galactic center following a close encounter\nwith Sgr A.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 12 Sep 2014 03:00:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-22"}
